flowchart TD
    Start([User: getTimeSyncVariant<br/>call])
    Start --> CheckInit{TSE<br/>initialized?}
    
    CheckInit -->|No| ErrorInit[Exception:<br/>ErrorDeviceNotInitialized]
    CheckInit -->|Yes| IdentifyVariant[Identify supported<br/>Time Synchronization Variant]
    
    IdentifyVariant --> CheckVariant{Which<br/>Variant?}
    
    CheckVariant -->|No updateTime<br/>Function| ReturnAuto[Return:<br/>automaticSync]
    CheckVariant -->|Only updateTime<br/>with Parameter| ReturnManual[Return:<br/>manualSync]
    CheckVariant -->|Both<br/>possible| ReturnBoth[Return:<br/>automaticAndManualSync]
    
    ReturnAuto --> End([End])
    ReturnManual --> End
    ReturnBoth --> End
    
    ErrorInit --> End
    
    style IdentifyVariant fill:#87CEEB
    style ReturnAuto fill:#FFD700
    style ReturnManual fill:#90EE90
    style ReturnBoth fill:#87CEEB
    
    Note1[automaticSync:<br/>Time is set centrally/automatically,<br/>NOT via API]
    ReturnAuto -.-> Note1
    
    Note2[manualSync:<br/>Time ONLY via API<br/>with updateTime Parameter]
    ReturnManual -.-> Note2
    
    Note3[automaticAndManualSync:<br/>Both possible]
    ReturnBoth -.-> Note3
